%F A004483 Periodic with period and saltus 3: a(n) = 3*floor(n/3) + ((n+2) mod 3).
%F A004483 a(n) = n + 2*cos(2*n*Pi/3). - _Wesley Ivan Hurt_, Sep 27 2017
%F A004483 From _R. J. Mathar_, Dec 14 2017: (Start)
